gemini-plugin-cc

This product includes software developed as a Claude Code plugin that wraps
Google's Gemini CLI (https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli).

The plugin architecture is a port of the structure used by openai/codex-plugin-cc
(Apache-2.0). Gemini and Google are trademarks of Google LLC. This project is not
